  <brief_title>Strawberries and Knee Osteoarthritis (OA)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Freeze-dried Strawberries on Systemic Markers of Inflammation and Knee Function in Participants With Osteoarthritis (OA)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
